#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:1
msgid "E4180"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `unsupported_match_strategy`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:5
msgid "Unsupported `lexmatch` match strategy."
msgstr "不支持的 `lexmatch` 匹配策略。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:7
msgid ""
"`lexmatch` only supports the default first-match strategy and the "
"explicit `longest` strategy. Other strategy names are rejected."
msgstr "`lexmatch` 只支持默认的首次匹配策略，以及显式的 `longest` 策略。其他策略名会被拒绝。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:11
msgid ""
"`lexmatch` is deprecated for new code. Prefer regex match expressions "
"such as `value =~ re\"...\"` unless you specifically need legacy lexer-"
"style behavior."
msgstr ""
"新代码中已不推荐使用 `lexmatch`。除非你确实需要旧式词法分析器风格的行为，否则请优先使用 `value =~ re\"...\"` "
"这类正则匹配表达式。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:15
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:17
msgid "The following example asks for an unsupported `shortest` strategy:"
msgstr "下面的示例请求了不支持的 `shortest` 策略："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:19
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn classify(input : String) -> String {\n"
"  lexmatch input with shortest {\n"
"    \"if\" => \"keyword\"\n"
"    _ => \"identifier\"\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  ignore(classify)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:23
msgid "MoonBit will report an error."
msgstr "MoonBit 会报告一个错误。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:25
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:27
msgid ""
"Use one of the supported strategies, or rewrite the code with a regex "
"match expression when first-match behavior is enough:"
msgstr "使用受支持的策略之一；如果首次匹配行为已经足够，也可以用正则匹配表达式重写代码："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4180.md:30
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"fn classify(input : String) -> String {\n"
"  if input =~ re\"^if$\" {\n"
"    \"keyword\"\n"
"  } else {\n"
"    \"identifier\"\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(classify(\"if\"), content=\"keyword\")\n"
"  inspect(classify(\"gift\"), content=\"identifier\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

